annotationA: Sodium-dependent serotonin transporter; Terminates the action of serotonin by its high affinity sodium-dependent reuptake into presynaptic terminals; Belongs to the sodium:neurotransmitter symporter (SNF) (TC 2.A.22) family
annotationB: Vesicular monoamine transporter is responsible for packaging the neurotransmitters dopamine, serotonin and octopamine into secretory vesicles
